data.value:
Rules:
You must select what you want to play (numbers or color).
If you select to play numbers, you have to choose six numbers in the range of 1 to 48. You need to hit all the numbers, but the position of your last hit number is the coefficient you get.
If you play colors, you have to select one color from the dropdown list. Every color is displayed on six balls, so again, you need to hit six balls right, and the coefficient is determined the same way.
